      "description": "Adds a bind mount for the data folder to a MinIO container resource.",
      "remarks": "Add an MinIO container to the application model and reference it in a .NET project. Additionally, in this\nexample a bind mount is added to the container to allow data to be persisted across container restarts.\n```\nvar builder = DistributedApplication.CreateBuilder(args);\nvar minio = builder.AddMinio(\"minio\")\n.WithDataBindMount(\"./data/minio/data\");\nvar api = builder.AddProject<Projects.Api>(\"api\")\n.WithReference(minio);\nbuilder.Build().Run();\n```",
      "returns": "The `IResourceBuilder`1`.",
      "kind": "Method",
      "signature": "withDataBindMount(source: string): MinioContainerResource",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "source",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "The source directory on the host to mount into the container."
        }
      ],
      "returnType": "MinioContainerResource",
      "returnsBuilder": true,
      "targetTypeId": "CommunityToolkit.Aspire.Hosting.Minio/Aspire.Hosting.ApplicationModel.MinioContainerResource",
      "expandedTargetTypes": [
        "Aspire.Hosting.ApplicationModel.MinioContainerResource"
      ]
